bindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104txw1665702714934.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/txw1665702714934.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/txw1665702714934.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"txw1665702714934\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Panel Position\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Position of the panel for a form or application shell when displayed at runtime.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"txw1665702714934__section_w5113ab1b5b1_w5114ab1b5_w5115ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"txw1665702714934__table_d11738e1_d11739e1_d11740e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"txw1665702714934__table_d11738e1_d11739e1_d11740e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"txw1665702714934__table_d11738e1_d11739e1_d11740e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txw1665702714934__table_d11738e1_d11739e1_d11740e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Default</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txw1665702714934__table_d11738e1_d11739e1_d11740e1__entry__2\">\n Default position for the platform\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txw1665702714934__table_d11738e1_d11739e1_d11740e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">T</code> (top) </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txw1665702714934__table_d11738e1_d11739e1_d11740e1__entry__2\">\n Top of the window\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txw1665702714934__table_d11738e1_d11739e1_d11740e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">B</code> (bottom) </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txw1665702714934__table_d11738e1_d11739e1_d11740e1__entry__2\">\n Bottom of the window\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txw1665702714934__table_d11738e1_d11739e1_d11740e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">R</code> (right) </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txw1665702714934__table_d11738e1_d11739e1_d11740e1__entry__2\">\n Right side of the window\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txw1665702714934__table_d11738e1_d11739e1_d11740e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">L</code> (left) </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txw1665702714934__table_d11738e1_d11739e1_d11740e1__entry__2\">\n Left side of the window\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txw1665702714934__table_d11738e1_d11739e1_d11740e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">F</code> (float) </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txw1665702714934__table_d11738e1_d11739e1_d11740e1__entry__2\">\n Panel can float freely\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"txw1665702714934__section_u5w_n5l_twb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d344104e152\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"txw1665702714934__table_d11744e1_d11745e1_d11746e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dynamic?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dependencies:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"txw1665702714934__section_opv_p5l_twb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d344104e201\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"txw1665702714934__p_d100430e1_d100431e1_d100432e1\">If you are defining components for use in multiple\n            operating environments, it is recommended that you not set this property, leaving it to\n            the default. The meaning of the definition depends on the GUI being used.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"txw1665702714934__section_mnf_r5l_twb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d344104e210\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"txw1665702714934__ul_p5v_r5l_twb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"txw1665702714934__li_d40511e1_d40512e1_d40513e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yye1705472567076.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yye1705472567076.html\" title=\"An application shell is the first object that is executed when a Windows or character mode application is started. It determines how the application is initialized and the first form component that is displayed.\">Application Shells for Desktop Applications</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"txw1665702714934__li_d40514e1_d40515e1_d40516e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"usl1704692305727.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/usl1704692305727.html\" title=\"Form components provide the user interface for Uniface desktop applications. They are always executed on the client system and can be modal (form retains focus until it is closed) or non-modal (users can switch focus to other forms).\">Forms</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616229\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616229\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Panel Position Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Panel Position Position of the panel for a form or application shell when displayed at runtime. Value Description Default Default position for the platform T (top) Top of the window B (bottom) Bottom of the window R (right) Right side of the window L (left) Left side of the window F (float) Panel can float freely Usage Dynamic? No Dependencies: None Description If you are defining components for use in multiple operating environments, it is recommended that you not set this property, leaving it to the default. The meaning of the definition depends on the GUI being used. Applies To Application Shells for Desktop Applications Forms Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}